  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Salesians of Don Bosco operate 5,000 schools and technical training centers, 23 colleges, 216 clinics and hospitals, 225 orphanages and shelters, and run a wide variety of social and economic development activities throughout the world. In each country, the Salesians combine the aspects of an orphanage, a school, a church, a children&apos;s recreation center, in addition to varied social programs.

This shipment will serve the Salesian work of the Parroquia la Divina Providencia (Divine Providence Parish) in Guatemala. The Parroquia la Divina Providencia runs a variety of programs including a primary school, two vocational training centers, a medical clinic and several child and youth development programs.</narrative>
